{"tid":1390131,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！ 有狗扮請人食飯 之後。。。。","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:13:23.000Z","uid":20948,"like":223,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d3231163f792a659d9921f14bfb450b688909305","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係上一個食飯Post樓主。Sorry for標題黨。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>有冇人一齊食飯呀？[遍地開花］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382296</a></em></span><br />\n上次一見到啲戰友冇飯食，心急如焚即刻留左TG，開埋個TG group。<br />\n同時瞬間入左過百個熱心嘅朋友，展開左激情對話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地都立即意識到問題：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼</span></span><br />\n我地好怕自己出於熱心，反而爲戰友招惹麻煩，於是我地慢慢討論建立左一套簡單系統，希望喺最大程度保障到大家安全情況下，俾戰友有飯食：<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>1. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰友做主導</span></em></span>：<br />\n我從來都唔同意呢個行動係施與受，亦都對「家長請細路食飯」呢個講法有啲反感。喺呢度我一概稱大家爲戰友。<br />\n我希望<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">由有需要嘅戰友做主導，想食咩，點食，一唔一齊食，都要尊重。<br />\n如果戰友想用八達通，HKTV Mall，Foodpanda，Deliveryroo等等嘅方式，或者入餐廳點完餐俾錢就走，我地都會尊重同支持。</span></span><br />\n當然，大家坐低一齊，同食不言，作爲一種沉默嘅陪伴，我個人都鼓勵。<br />\n如果有多幾個人，可以互相溝通一下，我地group都多人，絕對可以安排。<br />\n畢竟風雨飄搖，我地大家都需要用唔同方式互相扶持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>2. 登記驗證</em></span>：<br />\n我地準備左一份google form俾有心請食飯嘅朋友，登記TG，地區同埋<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">工作證明</span>等資料，（我地用證明文件+同白紙寫上TG cover敏感資料嘅方式）<br />\n從群組中挑選左幾名願意驗明正身嘅Admin出黎之後，由admin向每個登記人進行驗證。Admin亦會PM登記人double check一次。<br />\n驗證通過後，admin刪除登記人私隱，將TG加入已認證聯絡表入面。<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n(順帶一提，好多有心人竟然俾埋身份證，住址證明....我地都有提醒返呢啲朋友。網絡陷阱多，大家真係千奇唔好咁天真）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>3. Channel發佈</em></span>：<br />\n我地開左個Channel，公佈已認證嘅家長，俾戰友用TG聯絡。<br />\n同時有啲注意事項俾大家留意返。<br />\n例如絕對唔好過問/透露自己私隱同行蹤，去過邊，姓名等資料。<br />\n我地亦唔鼓勵食用住家飯，不明來歷嘅飯盒，亦唔好去偏僻地方。<br />\n希望去返啲正式食肆，避免<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食物中毒</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>4. 報平安</em></span>：<br />\n我地開左個報平安Group，如果有任何食飯/請食飯嘅手足，我地都希望佢地update我地，俾我地放心。而順利食完飯之後，我地會喺已驗證list入面mark返呢位手足請過幾次食飯，算係一個簡陋嘅信用系統。<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">目前爲止，我地已經驗證左70個想提供膳食嘅熱心人士，有老有幼。當然即使我地有驗證系統，都會儘量同各位朋友吹多幾句，但我地無法100%保證冇犬隻僞造文件嘗試滲入。所以唯有靠大家保持警惕。</span><br />\n<br />\n由於尚未宣傳，冇乜手足知道，但琴晚都有一個成功個案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqwa7up.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foqwa7up.jpg&h=b55685ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都知道，食物只係一小部分，前線要gear，要人，<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">我地知，我地真係知，我地都發夢。</span></span><br />\n但花左一晚整左呢個群組，希望佢留喺度發揮作用。<br />\n我地都可能會組織其他行動，幫得就幫。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">前路艱難，希望大家繼續守望相助，共同進退。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<br />\n最後，請各位戰友唔好餓親個肚！！<br />\n唔好覺得羞愧！爲正義而戰無需羞愧！<br />\n希望你地有需要嘅時候唔好怕醜，接受我地嘅元氣彈！！</span><br />\n<br />\nTG Channel Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/NoStarvingFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNoStarvingFront&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qndqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=3b67d2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/NoStarvingFront</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a232894b480df9c4ccc73fbfc786ca314f666eaf","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1bd1ddc901400c6498e668f1188e94ed061d2c","tid":1390131,"uid":88300,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"狗係正苦狗, 可以做假資料<br />\n好難防 捐GEAR到物資站最實際"},{"pid":"a8e6578672897348ae7a9eb085b625b9f90a17b1","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a85cf0c77d1786463d86f35e4b74ac44b5cf575","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0f1bd1ddc901400c6498e668f1188e94ed061d2c","tid":1390131,"uid":88300,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"狗係正苦狗, 可以做假資料<br />\n好難防 捐GEAR到物資站最實際"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"完全同意，所以只能靠人手filter完，再叮囑戰友小心行事"},{"pid":"39131447275b54414a20ffbbd4e8b38b3c41dfda","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d319b98870a574fdc09bcf9759fd37285cb3c6","tid":1390131,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a